mjc.jasmin

Class JasminGenerator

  • java.lang.Object
    • mjc.analysis.AnalysisAdapter
      • mjc.jasmin.JasminGenerator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Analysis, mjc.node.Switch

    public class JasminGenerator
extends AnalysisAdapter
    The JasminGenerator class generates Jasmin code from the AST.

    Construct an instance of the class with a JasminHandler for handling the output. Then call the generate(Node, SymbolTable, Map) method to start the generation.

      • generate

        public void generate(mjc.node.Node ast,
            SymbolTable symbolTable,
            java.util.Map types)
        Generates Jasmin code.

        The handle method of the JasminHandler passed in during construction will be called for each generated class.

        Parameters:
        ast - Input AST.
        symbolTable - Input symbol table.
        types - Input AST node to MiniJava type map.
